/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/fsh91g6znxauetpkgukk 440w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/xvo4lnzbbs8ej7clm11g 550w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/yzf0rrvwbw9hgsxjmdj0 660w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/soongogghtd1bhavy8l9 770w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/vl4x9bfetpuyp2c9u0tu 880w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/zkq6vniyaqj3951tdbup 990w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/lsgrrrutqxzj7ipwb3qk 1056w"></figure><p></p><p>同样，在这个例子中，任务中不再涉及字母顺序（同样，适合指令类型模型，但可以通过多镜头提示轻松适应基本模型），有一系列步骤似乎被用来最终预测一个“K”或“k”标记...... </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/jqszxlqzsop5qnjnptl5" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/a3jj14mmw3mpdzxgu4dd 110w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/f6ylj9evhzlr44qo3ttt 220w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/xfg0hpaaqqnm2d4ll65m 330w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/m890nc14zzo8wb3k8nxx 440w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/kawwamivcf3umkmzk6nw 550w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/sizn7x3qfwn82fkujun8 660w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaD