>以各种方式重新设计此提示可能会导致“Y”输出，但尚未找到能够在大量（标记、字母）对中始终成功完成此任务的单标记输出提示格式。</figcaption></figure><h2><br>解决方案：关注首字母信息</h2><p>不管“思想链”解释的真实性如何，由于无法通过单次前向传递获得像样的字母存在任务结果，导致决定将重点放在 26 个类似的“首字母”任务上。这些涉及对标记进行分类，不是根据它们是否包含“k”或“K”，而是根据它们是否<i>以“k”或“K”开头</i>（忽略任何前导空格）。训练 26 个相关线性探针，同样没有真正的超参数调整，导致了更好的 F1 结果： </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/bnbtxdgqtpw6d3umulsv" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/luno2ojsj6ahutobjczn 120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/lagj7ooza6k4npuqwgju 240w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/qpw3fokqj940stsq7d3x 360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/f6vzcfnigonlxhmz6tys 480w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/dzbpl17vfllgwb1fiku8 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/y16gumimttqwede3tzrx 720w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/vgcacyainzs8dcakeqzn 840w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/me4mjntvg7zyp7axyxzm 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/jdkyayvquuaruuc5y4xc 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/yxf1ncrgpitdx4cbpqki 1172w"><figcaption>线性探针的 F1 分数是在整个 46893 个“全罗马”GPT-J 标记集上计算的（即过滤掉那些包含除前导空格之外的非字母字符的标记）。</figcaption></figure><p><br>以下多镜头提示模板满足了我们通过单次前向传递（即单令牌输出）引出 GPT-J 的首字母知识的要求：</p><pre> <code>The string &quot; heaven&quot; begins with the letter &quot;H&quot; The string &quot; same&quot; begins with the letter &quot;S&quot; The string &quot; peace&quot; begins with the letter &quot;</code></pre><p>然而，我们不再处理像“字符串 &#39;&lt;token>;&#39; 是否包含字母 &#39;&lt;letter>;&#39; 这样的二元问题？这里的任务不是二元分类，而是“预测字符串 &#39;&lt; 中的第一个字母” token>;&#39;&quot;。因此，对于初始的基于探针的方法，我们将简单地<strong>计算 26 个探针向量之间的余弦相似度，而不是直接应用与我们的首字母线性探针相关的 26 个二元分类器中的任何一个和 token 嵌入向量，然后选择最大的</strong>。这将为我们提供对 token 字符串的第一个字母的预测。</p><p>用简单的几何术语来说，如果嵌入向量<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{x}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>与“P”首字母探测向量的对齐程度大于与其他 25 个首字母探测向量中的任何一个的对齐程度，则我们将预测<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{x}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的标记字符串以“p”或“P”开头。<br><br>尽管最初只是权宜之计，但事实证明，远离二进制任务很重要，因为错误模式（在基于提示或基于探测的方法预测错误首字母的标记中）似乎揭示了有关机制的某些信息涉及 GPT 拼写功能，我们将在下面看到。<br></p><h3>与探针向量的余弦相似度</h3><p>令人放心的是，对于每个首字母探测向量，其嵌入与其具有最大余弦相似度的标记列表将只包含以相关字母开头的标记（此处较大的字体大小对应于更大的余弦相似度，并且不包括前导空格） : </p><figure class="table"><table><tbody><tr><td><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:99.49%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ojc7bln5ydnaq3u7q4yl" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/lwuh5a30ms4gyb0ytdix 90w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/d5amyrdhxddp9ure9jax 180w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/codrc0rst7rr13pcgvcq 270w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/so9dauqz7xaawqbhtfvb 360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/gsryva6ijaghh1bq8xwd 450w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/njpocsbazpib6ov03scr 540w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ppns7f5mlcefistxh6br 630w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/bh0xqlqs5wrcvqndpgbl 720w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/kregvc6wptzx4qqmdd0e 810w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/n057aflqjgxxiveileki 826w"></figure></td><td><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:100%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/iualjzlyvyb5aawcslfm" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/fgyvkvxnihvdoi0jzpmp 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/hgkmmv3mv1zoss5laneq 230w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/mggmlnvp4jf1cfvwz1dm 310w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/bebonbssddptraxmpkex 390w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/pygmywd4k7dmcqag9u6n 470w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/Gya