参考，以下是每个字母（大写或小写）开头的标记数量：</p><pre> <code>{&#39;A&#39;: 4085, &#39;B&#39;: 2243, &#39;C&#39;: 4000, &#39;D&#39;: 2340, &#39;E&#39;: 2371, &#39;F&#39;: 1838, &#39;G&#39;: 1334, &#39;H&#39;: 1531, &#39;I&#39;: 2929, &#39;J&#39;: 492, &#39;K&#39;: 555, &#39;L&#39;: 1612, &#39;M&#39;: 2294, &#39;N&#39;: 1032, &#39;O&#39;: 1935, &#39;P&#39;: 3162, &#39;Q&#39;: 200, &#39;R&#39;: 2794, &#39;S&#39;: 4266, &#39;T&#39;: 2126, &#39;U&#39;: 1293, &#39;V&#39;: 824, &#39;W&#39;: 1165, &#39;X&#39;: 78, &#39;Y&#39;: 252, &#39;Z&#39;: 142}</code></pre><p><br> GPT-J 令牌嵌入作为模糊超球面壳分布在 4096 维空间中，其中心（平均嵌入或“质心”）与原点的欧几里德距离为 1.7158，绝大多数嵌入与此具有欧几里德距离质心大约在 0.9 到 1.1 之间。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:83.64%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/rsi9wodhb9gkibro7wbv" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/rzd9b3ccl0w18azvnbc8 100w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/nsktjvpvpffoajbngyzd 200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/berczg31st9xsnb5k2bb 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ncejy3hzesatp2zkvudu 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/yf5mio26u2oej8zclb5p 500w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/gmgoukhuylfuj0obgvga 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ww0acv715mom9cvke1fe 700w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/qz2p3ilq8zqabldug0vm 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc4